With Freeze:
Hotkeys on F2 ~ F5:
Title Cooldown + Freeze.ahk Sourcefile
Title Cooldown + Freeze.exe Application
Reset timer: F9
Close app: F12

Hotkey on Numpad1 ~ Numpad4 (Num pad, 1; 2; 3; 4):
Title Cooldown + Freeze_Num.ahk Sourcefile
Title Cooldown + Freeze_Num.exe Application
Reset timer: NumEnter
Close app: NumSub (Minus, -)

-----------------------

Without Freeze:
Hotkeys on F2 ~ F4:
Title Cooldown.ahk Sourcefile
Title Cooldown.exe Application
Reset timer: F9
Close app: F12

Hotkey on Numpad1 ~ Numpad3 (Num pad, 1; 2; 3):
Title Cooldown_Num.ahk Sourcefile
Title Cooldown_Num.exe Application
Reset timer: NumEnter
Close app: NumSub (Minus, -)